        <updated>2025-10-24T00:00:00.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[Welcome to the official blog of Perseverance Technology! We’re excited to share our work in innovation. Now we're introducing our flagship product: Unicorn Solution.]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Welcome to the official blog of <strong>Perseverance Technology</strong>! We’re excited to share our work in innovation. Now we're introducing our flagship product: <strong>Unicorn Solution</strong>.
At Perseverance Technology, our goal is simple: build technology that matters. Unicorn Solution is the result of this mission—a market-ready safety system designed for Heavy Goods Vehicles (HGVs).</p>
<p>It's an advanced camera monitoring application that addresses critical <strong>MOIS</strong> (Moving Off Information System) and <strong>BSIS</strong> (Blind Spot Information System) requirements, fully compliant with <strong>UN R151</strong> and <strong>UN R159</strong>. What sets it apart? It achieves all this using a <strong>single fisheye camera</strong> paired with powerful <strong>AI-based detection</strong>.</p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="inside-unicorn-solution">Inside Unicorn Solution<a href="https://perseverance-tech-tw.github.io/unicorn-solution-doc/blog/welcome#inside-unicorn-solution" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Inside Unicorn Solution" title="Direct link to Inside Unicorn Solution" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>Unicorn Solution is a complete visualization platform designed for safety and operational efficiency. Its key features include:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Live View Mode</strong>: A real-time monitoring system with various display layouts, including MOIS, BSIS, Panorama, and Original.</li>
<li><strong>Playback Mode</strong>: Displays all recorded results from Live View, allowing users to review and analyze past footage.</li>
<li><strong>Configuration Mode</strong>: Allows users to adjust camera parameters, display preferences, and system behavior.</li>
<li><strong>Setting Mode</strong>: Enables customization of operational settings, including Camera Parameters, Resolution, and Language.</li>
<li><strong>Help Mode</strong>: Provides guidance on the functions of all buttons in the interface to help users understand the system.</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="join-us-on-the-journey">Join Us on the Journey<a href="https://perseverance-tech-tw.github.io/unicorn-solution-doc/blog/welcome#join-us-on-the-journey" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Join Us on the Journey" title="Direct link to Join Us on the Journey" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>Stay tuned for fresh updates, deep dives, and stories from the people behind the work. This blog will be your hub for updates, technical insights, and support for Unicorn Solution.</p>
<p>Thank you for being part of this community—together, we’ll build great things!</p>
<p>Sincerely,<br>
<!-- -->Perseverance Technology</p>]]></content>
