        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>At Perseverance Technology, we believe that great technology is built by great people. Our mission is to "build technology that matters," and one of the clearest embodiments of that mission is the <strong>Unicorn Solution</strong>.</p>
<p>While we work on many other innovative projects, in this documentation, we want to introduce you to the software engineers who are core to the development of the <strong>Unicorn Solution</strong>. They are the problem-solvers, innovators, and builders dedicated to delivering the best solution.</p>
<p>Let's meet the incredible team behind this product.</p>
